            "anno_id": 1,
            "text": "where  $\\mathbf{u}_j^i \\in \\mathbb{R}^d$ . Moreover, we denote all the utterance representations in the history conversation  $H^i$  by  $\\mathbf{U}^i = {\\mathbf{u}_1^i, \\mathbf{u}_2^i, \\cdots, \\mathbf{u}_{n_i}^i} \\in \\mathbb{R}^{n_i \\times d}$ , where  $n_i$  is the turn number of  $H^i$ . Next, we apply a",
            "line_with_spans": [
                {
                    "category_type": "text_span",
                    "poly": [
                        1270,
                        3007.5,
                        2202.5,
