            "poly": [
                1267.5,
                2327.5,
                2192.5,
                2327.5,
                2192.5,
                2820,
                1267.5,
                2820
            ],
            "ignore": false,
            "order": 12,
            "anno_id": 1,
            "text": "Specifically, for a history conversation session  $H^i = \\{h_1^i, h_2^i, \\cdots, h_{n_i}^i\\}$ , we first prepend a special token \"User:\" or \"Assistant:\" to each utterance  $h_j^i$  in  $H^i$  depending on the role of the utterance speaker, and then pad all utterances to the same length  $l_{utter}$ . For each utterance  $h_j^i$ , we apply an embedding layer  $E_m$ ,  $n_{enc}$  Transformer encoder layers, and a Max-pooling layer to obtain its dense representation as follows,",
            "line_with_spans": [
                {
                    "category_type": "text_span",
                    "poly": [
                        1267.5,
                        2327.5,
                        2192.5,
                        2327.5,
